author: Dana Howl
description:
Head to https://squarespace.com/danahowl to save 10% off your first purchase of a website or domain using code DANAHOWL

To celebrate the release of the new Emperor's Children faction, I thought I would paint up a Daemon Princess that had been sitting in my collection unpainted for some time now. I explore quite a lot of techniques in this video, from glazing and gradients to non-metallic metals and volcanic basing! 

My Website: https://howlcorp.com
Support Me on PATREON: https://patreon.com/danahowl
